highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Guwahati. “Jhoome Jo Pathaan” is the highest at #3.
“Flowers” by Miley Cyrus is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Guwahati, up 35 spots at #12.
“Tu Aake Dekhle” by King has been on Top Songs Guwahati the longest, at 68 weeks straight.
“Tu Mile Dil Khile” by Asees Kaur and Stebin Ben is the highest new entry on Top Songs Guwahati at #31.
